      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·010.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Seaou sing.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>嘒彼小星，三五在東，肅肅宵征，夙夜在公，寔命不同。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Small are those starlets,
Three or five of them in the east.
Swiftly by night we go ;
In the early dawn we are with the prince.
Our lot is not like hers.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
