      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·010.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Seaou sing.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>嘒彼小星，維參與昴，肅肅宵征，抱衾與裯，寔命不猶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Small are those starlets,
And there are Orion and the Pleiades.
Swiftly by night we go,
Carrying our coverlets and sheets.
Our lot is not as hers.</seg>
      </tuv>
